{
  "stem": "7506.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "The-- also-- other thing my mother did was, in retrospect, very important.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Although at that time, I didn't know why I needed to know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "She make my sister and I memorize [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the address of my-- [SOBBING] of my grandmother in England.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We memorized that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And of course, I know it to this day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] At the time, I didn't see why we needed to know that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But in actual fact, as time progressed, it was important that I did know it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So she made us memorize the mother's address, the grandmother's address.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I don't remember how long we lived in the Jewish quarter.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I do remember that middle of the night when they came to fetch us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "That, I do remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had no-- from what I recall, I had no friends there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At this time, I was about 10-- 10 and a bit--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "10 And a bit.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My sister, a year younger than me, nine and a bit.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- my mother or father must have woken us up in the middle of night-- about 3 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know if it was 3 o'clock, but it was in the middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she said we had to get dressed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember we had-- my mother made us put on double underwear, double socks, and pack our rucksacks.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember there was a lot of shouting in the street, and lights.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And all kinds of vehicles.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And and what they had in Germany, the Germans, was the Grune Polizei, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] all in green.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they come up the stairs with guns.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they-- and they made us get out of the house.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
